mesiddoniacho sonvsarik kirt zoddil'lo somratt. mesiddoniacho raza filip ani tachi poili ranni elimpios hancho put. pela hanga zolm'. bhurgeponnant filipan taka iuvrazak favo tem loskori ani rajki xikxonn dilem. tacho guru oeristtottol hannem taka piraiechea tera te solla vorsancher kavio, kola, rajioxastr ani totvginean hea vixeanchi goddi laili. homorcho akilizh ho tacho adorx axil'lo. taka lagun olekjhanddoran sobond zog jikhcheli khor itsa ballgili ani te promann sodanch choddhaiechem dhoronn apnnailem.

i.so. poilim 336 vorsa filipacho khun zalo. olekjhanddor piraiechea visavea vorsa mesiddonche gadier boslo. tache poilim i. so. poilim 340 vorsa filipan jen'na baizhonttiomocher dhuri ghal'li ten'na olekjhanddoran mesiddoniachi rakhonn kel'li ani middi lokancho porabhov kel'lo. fuddem tannem filip haka grik nogrorajiosonghacher zoit mellovpak palov dilo.

razasonacher bostokoch eka vorsa bhitor olekjhanddoran ut'torek ddeniub nhoim ani ostontek eddriettik hanga meren apli sot'ta vaddoili. thibiz rajeacher ghuri ghalun khub nagrikank tannem marlem. kaim zannank gulam' mhunn vikle. thoinchim devllam ani aplem avddichea pinddor kovichem ghor soddun her soglleo bandavolli matiebhorovnn keleo. hacho porinnam' mhunn othens xar apunn zavn xoronn ailem. magir tannem somrid'dh ani bollixtt oxa iranni samrajeacher ghuri ghalpacho nixchev kelo. iranni lokank xasokamvixim svaminxttha naxil'li. hacho olekjhanddoran bhorpur faido ghetlo.

i.so. poilim 334 vorsa grisantlea mukhel suvatincher rakhnne khatir soinio dovrun olekjhanddoran dadnils nhoim humpli. tachea soineant parmenio, ttolemi, anttigonos, seliukos,niarkos sarke xur ani onnbhovi senapoti axil'le. te bhair aplem svotachem xovroi, dhaddos, chikatti hea gunnank lagun olekjhanddor aplea soinikank deva bhoxen axil'lo. sumar 40,000 chem soinio ghevn olekjhanddoran iranncher ghuri ghali. ddoraisan dhaddil'lea senapotincho greniks nhoinche deger porabhov korun to siriuavotten gelo. thoim isoschea akhata kodden tachem ddoraisachea vixal soineakodden zhuz zalem. olekjhanddoran ddoraisocho porabhov kelo. magir tannem finixion armar hataslem. ijiptacher om'mol bosovn olekjhanddria xarachi thaponnuk keli.tannem gogamila hanga ddoraisocho anik ekdam porabhov kelo. ddorais zhuzamollantlean pollun gelo. oxe toren olekjhanddor iranni samrajeacho odhipoti zalo. tannem i.so. poilim 331 vorsa irannchi (tea rituntli) rajdhani bebilon hanga mottea dobajean provex kelo. fuddem tannem spusa ani porsepolis heo ani her rajdhaneo kabiz korun thoinche khojine luttle. porsepolis rajvaddo lasun grisacher irannan ghal'le ghuriecho sudd ghetlo.

survek olekjhanddoracho ud'dex fokot iranni soineacho vidhvons korop hoch zavn axil'lo. punn ek sarkea mellot ravil'lea zoitank lagun samrajio sthapnechi tachi itsa vaddik lagli. techpori tem samrajio sasnnachem tigun urchem mhunn jikhil'lea prodexank appolo dhorm' ani riti-rivaz, chali toxench kaim raxttri-i sonsthai rakunk tannem porvanogi dili. aplea nanvachim solla 'olekjhanddria' nogram tannem bandlim.

iranni ani grik lokanchem songhotton korche khatir apunn svota ddoraisoche dhuve kodden logn zalo ani aplea vangoddchea her senadhikareank legit iranni bailam kodden logn korpacho agro korpak laglo. iranni ghoddesvoranche pongodd toiar kele. apunn svota iranni bhes ghalpak laglo. iranni lok razak dev mantale tosoch soglleamni apleak man divcho, apleak saxttang nomskar korcho oso prochar tannem suru kelo. kaim mesiddonion soinikank hem pottlemna. tamnni olekjhanddoraadd kott rochlo. to kott uktaddar ailo ani tannem kott korotleank mornnachi kheast dili. i. so. poilim 328 vorsa tannem bekttria ani tache ut'techo sogddiana he prodex jikhle. thoinche rajkumvori kodden logn zalo ani uprant hindukux humpun i. so. poilinchea 327, me mhoineant bharotacher ghuri ghali.

bhartantlea thoddea razamni olekjhanddorak fattboll dilem. ponjabant tea kallant kaim lhan razosot'tak rajeam ani kaim gonnrajeam axil'lim. tamnni apli svotontrotai rakhpa khatir vhodda xovrean zhuz dilem ani magiruch olekjhanddorak fuddem sorpak vatt meklli zali. tachea xovreacheo kotha tea vellar grik lekhkamni borovn dovorleat.

olekjhanddoran kabul nhoinche deger don senapotink borench soinio divn puxkolavti razacher dhaddlem ani apnne svota kunar, ponjkhor ani svat nhoianchea degnnantlean chal keli. thoim taka ospesioi ani osorkenoi (oxvok) hea dongramni raupi pongddam kodden zhuzchem poddlem.hea zhuzant olekjhanddor zokhmi zalo ani tiddki bhitor tannem thoinchea sogllea lokanchi kot'tol korpacho hukum' dilo.

sindhu nhoim humpun to tokxoxilek pavlo. tokxoxilacho raza ambhi taka xoronn ailo. punn jhelom' ani chinab hanchea modlea vattharacher rajio korpi poros razan taka protikar kelo. dogaimmodim jhelomchea kamchhar akant zhuz pettlem. porsachi porabhov zalo. olekjhanddorak bharoti-i zhuzareanchea xovroiacho thavo laglo. porsa sarko xur zhuzari aplo palvi aslear chodd borem zatlem hea hetan olekjhanddoran tachem rajio taka porot dilem ani te bhair anikoi 15 gonnrajeancho mulukh tache suvadin kelo.

magir to bias nhoinche votten fuddem sorlo. vatter taka glovknikoi ani kothoioi (kott) hea gonnrajeam kodden zhuzchem poddlem. olekjhanddoroche soinik bias nhoim fuddem vochpak toiar naxil'le. biasafuddem gelear tankam nond razachea vixal soinea kodden loddtte poddttolem axil'lem. nond razachea xovreachi khobor taka guptheramvor vim mellil'li. te bhair atth-dha vorsanchea dis-rat eksarkea zhuzam uprant tankam visov zai axil'lo. olekjhanddoran poros haka jhelom' ani bias nhoim modlea prodexacho odhipoti nemun i. so. poilinchea februvari 326 t porot vochpacho nirnnoi ghetlo.

olekjhanddor ayil'lea margan porot gelo. jhelom' ani chinab nhoianchea songoma kodden taka malou (mol'loi) ani kxudrok (eksiddrokoi) hea songham kodden loddhai korchi poddli.malovanchea doreka nogorant taka khor protikar zalo. anik ek nogor ghetna olekjhanddor zokhmi zalo. tea vellar tachea tiddklea soinikamni bailam-bhurgeanchi krur kot'tol keli.

i. so. po. 325 chea sopttemborant olekjhanddor sindhu nhoinchea degevoilea pattol ganvant pavlo. thoinchean niarkoschea hatasokoil kaim soinio divn taka udka margan dhaddlo ani apunn bhuim-imargan boluchistamnatlean irannantlea siusa hanga i.so.po. 324 vorsa pavlo, siusa hanga taka moronn ailem.

olekjhanddor ho sonvsarantlo ek osadaronn zhuzari ani senamukheli zavn gelo. svodexa savn hozaramni moil ontravelea ogoneat prodexant tannem khub porakrom' korun zoitam zoddlim. purai goneat zogachem gris adhipotea sokoil ek raxttr zanvchem oxi tachi upatt itsa axil'li. punn tachea mornnak lagun ti purai zalina. ten'nachi iranni sundri roksenas ani ddoraischi dhuv barjhin heo tacheo don ranneo axil'leo. tachea mornna uprant roksenas he tache bailen zolmak ayil'lea choleachem nanv olekjhanddoruch dovorlem.

olekjhanddoran bharotacher kel'le ghuriek lagun bharotacho ostont dexankodden lagincho sombond ievn vepar ani samskritik sombond suru zale. olekjhanddora vangdda ayil'lea senapotimni ani grik lekhkamni boroil'lea grontham velean bharotachi borich mhaiti ostont dexamni pavli ani oxe toren bharotache siriua, mesiddonia, ijipt hea dexankodden rajonitik sombond suru zale

